title: Ranked Team casual
body:
Hey people,

Just looking for a casual ranked team to begin with that might develop into something more. Please fill out the form below.

If interested please comment your:
-Summoner Name
-Rank
-Preferred Position(s)
-Age
-Favourite Champions

Thanks

If its just casual then:
-SkiBorg
- Bronze (only like to play ranked in a duo at least)
- (In order) Jungle, Mid, Top
-16

 Top: Darius, Irelia
so yeah thats me i can play games with you if you want to see
